    ],
    "text": "\u0baa \u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b87\u0bb1\u0ba3\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bc8\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 (www.police.lk) \u0baa\u0b9a\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bc8 \u0bcd \u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9a\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb1\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd, \u201c\u0baa \u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bca \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf \u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc2\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd\u201d (Tell Inspector General Of Police) (https://telligp.police.lk) \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bc8 \u0b87\u0bb1\u0ba3\u0baf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0bca\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc8\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd (telligp@police.gov.lk) \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9\u0b9e\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bc8\u0bca\u0bbf \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 \u0bcd \u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0ba4\u0b95\u0bc8\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb1\u0bb3 \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0b9a\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9 \u0bcd \u0bc1\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0bca\u0b95 \u0baa \u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b9a\u0b9a\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0bb1\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bb2\u0bca\u0bae\u0bcd. \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa \u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bc8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bca\u0bbf\u0bc8\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b95\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b95\u0bca\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbf\u0b9a\u0bc8\u0ba9\u0bcd. \u0baa \u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0b9f\u0b95 \u0bcd \u0bbf\u0bca\u0bbf\u0bc8\u0bc1",
    "fonts": [
      "Kavivanar-Regular"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      45.47,
      398.35,
      58.75
    ],
    "text": "Public Awareness on the \u201cTell IGP\u201d Public Complaints Service",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      73.33,
      526.42,
      128.01
    ],
    "text": "The \u201cTell IGP\u201d initiative, introduced and implemented by the Sri Lanka Police, enables members of the public to directly submit complaints to the Inspector General of Police regarding any incident through an online platform. This programme is scheduled to be upgraded and re-launched in 2026 with further improvements.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      142.45,
      526.09,
      169.53
    ],
    "text": "Under this service, both local and foreign individuals are able to lodge complaints in Sinhala, Tamil, or English via a fully integrated online system.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      184.09,
      526.31,
      238.77
    ],
    "text": "Through the \u201cTell IGP\u201d platform, the public may directly provide information to the Inspector General of Police concerning organized crime and drug trafficking whether domestic or international as well as report offences, various grievances, traffic violations, public disturbances, and incidents of bribery or corruption.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      253.36,
      526.26,
      321.84
    ],
    "text": "Complaints received through this system are referred by the respective divisional officers to the relevant police stations, and investigating officers are promptly assigned to take necessary action. In instances where a complainant believes that appropriate action has not been taken, the system also provides an opportunity to re-escalate the matter directly to the Inspector General of Police.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      336.28,
      526.42,
      390.96
    ],
    "text": "Members of the public can access this service by visiting the official police website (www.police.lk) and navigating to the e-services section. Complaints and information may be submitted through the web portal \u201cTell Inspector General of Police\u201d (https://telligp.police.lk) or via email at telligp@police.gov.lk.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      405.54,
      526.13,
      432.62
    ],
    "text": "We kindly request media institutions to disseminate this information to enhance public awareness of the service.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
